# Self-deploy artifacts — running `deploy.sh .` (or deploying into the kit root)
# writes the kit's output into this repo. The canonical SOURCE lives under golden/;
# these root copies are deploy output, not source, and must not be committed.
/.claude/
/agent_docs/
/compound-engineering.local.md
/tasks/
/CLAUDE.md
/AGENTS.md

# Per-deploy state + tooling output
.blueprint-kit-version
blueprint-kit-manifest.json
.gitnexus/

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
*.swp
